text.text: Masjid Maroof is a good mosque. The weather is also good. Inside and outside are well-maintained, and there is also parking available on the roadside.

text.text:
Excellent design mosque, this is one of the worship place that is wide, well cleaned carpet, well decorated and always has safety features along the way. It now has multiple prayer halls, much more conducive and has such a beautiful interior
Calm when you start your night prayers. Bright and cool lights too.

text.text:
A fairly new mosque of 4/5 years. Well nestled at the corner of Boon Lay Ave. The interiors are very beautiful and the environment is very well-maintained by the friendly volunteers. It is also perfect for car owners as the parking is aplenty by the streetwise. Masya Allah.

Will recommend for those who are near to the area.
